name: Goychay and Zanzibar - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Goychay and Zanzibar - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Put on Goychay for a deep red look and mix it up with Zanzibar for a cool nude nail with a slight shimmer.

Goychay is a warm, deep red. Goychay is inspired by the Azerbaijani city famous for its pomegranate festival which features a parade with dances and music, a marketplace with artists displaying their work, and an exhibition of different pomegranate dishes and products.

Zanzibar is a cool, light nude with a barely-there shimmer. This cool nude is inspired by the Tanzanian Islands of Zanzibar. Zanzibar is famous for its rich history, endangered and unique animals, and it’s stunning sandy beaches.

name: Jakarta and Brunei - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Jakarta and Brunei - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Wear Jakarta for a pretty light purple that goes well with any skin tone and add Brunei for a fun silver shine.

Jakarta is a soft violet color. It is the largest city and capital of Indonesia and is considered one of the biggest melting pots of the Asian world. This violet color is inspired by the purple domes of the At-Tin Mosque and the violet lights of the bustling urban city in Indonesia.

Brunei is a vivid silver with a metallic foil finish. This metallic silver is inspired by the fifth richest nation in the world, Brunei. One of the traditional forms of art in this country is silverwork or silver crafting, an ancient practice that is now known to be a profitable industry for the cottages.

name: Pink Nail Polish Set (3 Piece)
description:
This pink nail polish set contains 3 beautiful shades of pink nail polish colors that work well with any outfit for all occasions!

Casablanca is a pearly light pink shade which was inspired by the beautiful architecture at the Hassan II Mosque in Casablanca, Morocco.

name: Dakar and Malé - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Dakar and Malé - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Dakar is a beautiful nude pink that also is great for the base color of creative nail art designs. Malé's bright blue will make you feel like you are on an island vacation in the Maldives.

Dakar is a nude with a light pink, rosy tone. This pretty light pink is inspired by Dakar, Senegal and its pink Lake Retba, also fondly called "Lac Rose" or "Lake Rose". The lake gets its pink hue from an algae that produces a red pigment, and is at its most vivid during the dry seasons.

Malé is a bright cobalt blue that has an opaque finish in just one coat. This bright blue is inspired by the Indian Ocean surrounding Malé, Maldives - an island nation known for its surfing, resorts, and scuba diving as well as its mosques and colorful buildings.

name: Agra and Dubai - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Agra and Dubai - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Apply Agra to get a glossy bold red and create a glamorous design by using Dubai's metallic gold.

Agra is a classic bold red, perfectly opaque in just one coat. This red nail polish was inspired by the red sandstone walls of the Agra Fort in Agra, India. The Agra Fort comprises of beautiful architecture such as the Jahangir Palace, the Khas Mahal, Diwan-I-Khas, and two beautiful mosques.

Dubai is a vivid and opaque metallic gold with a shimmer. This rich gold of Dubai is inspired by the Gold Sauk of its namesake. The gold market is one of the most popular destinations of the Emirates - with the city being known for its gold.

name: Isfahan and Azores - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Isfahan and Azores - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:

name: Istanbul and Bahrain - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Istanbul and Bahrain - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Who doesn't want a deep red nail on occasion? Istanbul is the perfect choice. Then switch it up with Bahrain by applying it alone or in a thin coat over a light blue or pink polish.

Istanbul is a deep maroon shad that provides full coverage in one swipe. Istanbul is inspired by the vibrant reds of the Turkish city: the beautiful red walls of the Hagia Sofia, the low red lighting of the basilica cistern, and the reds of spices and souvenirs in the spice market and grand bazaar.

Bahrain is an iridescent and a pearly color. This lovely iridescent polish was inspired by the sovereign state of Bahrain. Throughout history, Bahrain has been famous for its pearl trade and pearl diving, which inspired this pearly and iridescent color.

breadcrumbs.name: Karachi and Tripoli - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Use Karachi for a shimmery green glow and use Tripoli for a shimmery nude sparkle! A perfect set for those who can never have too much shimmer.

Karachi is a deep evergreen color with an iridescent finish. This deep evergreen color is inspired by the cosmopolitan city of Karachi, Pakistan and the green of the Pakistan flag. Karachi is also one of the most populous and fastest growing cities in the world.

name: Granada and Shiraz - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Granada and Shiraz - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Love purple nails? This set is for you. You can also use either Granada or Shiraz for a beautiful base color with a flower nail art design.

Granada is a light but opaque lavender purple. This color is inspired by the lavenders found all over the beautiful Spanish city, Granada. These flowers can be found growing along the path beside the citadel, covering the hills of the mountainous Andalusia, and coat the gardens of the Alhambra Palace.

Shiraz is a dark fuchsia with a purple undertone. This vibrant fuchsia is inspired by the "Pink Mosque" of Shiraz, Iran - Nasir al-Mulk Mosque. The mosque is adorned with stunning stained glass, Persian rugs, intricate painted tiles, and a concave style of architecture.

name: Pink Nail Polish Set (6 Piece)

Petra is a soft pink nude color. Petra is an incredible pre-historic city in Jordan, one of the wonders of the world.

name: Top Coat Clear and Zhangye - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Top Coat Clear and Zhangye - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Use Top Coat Clear with any color to get a glossy look. Perfect especially with Zhangye to give your nails a bright orange shine over Zhangye's semi matte finish!

Top Coat Clear is a quick-drying breathable nail polish which provides a protective seal over your color to prevent chipping and adds a glossy finished look to your nails.

Zhangye is a soft, creamsicle orange with a warm undertone. This beautiful coral is inspired by The Rainbow Mountains of China found at the Zhangye Danxia Landform Geological Park.

name: Sakura and Aswan - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Sakura and Aswan - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Sakura and Aswan are a cute combination and never go out of style. Nude nails will always be on trend, so you can't go wrong with this set!

Sakura is best described as a muted pink nude, nearly opaque with two coats. Sakura is inspired by the stunning pale pink cherry blossoms found in Sakura, Japan. In fact, the most common of all the cherry blossoms are called "Sakura" or Japanese Cherry.

Aswan is best described as a rich, opaque cocoa brown. Aswan is inspired by the historical city of Aswan, Egypt. In Aswan you will find Abu Simbel, incredible massive rock temples that were built by Ramesses II.

name: Himalayas and Meta - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Himalayas and Meta - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
A must-have set in your nail polish collection. Apply Himalayas for a unique pink tone and use Meta to give your nails that shiny red sparkle!

Himalayas is a salmon pink with a peach undertone. This perfect pink nude color is inspired by the pink rock salt mined near the Himalayan mountains of Punjab, Pakistan. The Himalayan pink salt is found in the Khewra Salt Mine.

Meta is a sprightly, deep red shimmer nail polish. Meta is inspired by Caño Cristales, the Colombian river also known as the "liquid rainbow" and "river of five colors," which is found in Meta, Columbia.

description:

Kashmir is best described as an opaque dusk pink with a slightly purple tone. Kashmir is inspired by Kashmir's traditional tea, Kashmiri chai and the pink blossoms and tulips of the Mughal Gardens.

Pretoria is best described as a deep, dark plum color. This deep plum nail polish is inspired by the purple Jacaranda trees of the South Africa capital, Pretoria. These beautiful trees drape the city in a gorgeous display of color.

breadcrumbs.name: Marrakech and Tuscany - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Marrakech and Tuscany together make up beautiful colors for a variety of fabulous designs! You can wear these nail polish colors all year round.

Marrakech is a bright and bold red-orange color. The vibrant city of Marrakech, Morocco inspired this fiery red. Nicknamed the "rose city" or the "red city," Marrakech's building and ramparts are made of an orange-red clay and chalk that coats the city in a red hue at sunset.

Tuscany is a burnt sienna with red undertone. This lovely burnt sienna shade is inspired by the Italian region of Tuscany, the fifth largest region in Italy. The terracotta clay rooftops of Tuscan homes inspired this nail polish color name.

name: Nizwa and Baghdad - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Nizwa and Baghdad - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Use Nizwa for a bright baby pink color and add Baghdad for a pretty, nude nail. These two light colors are sure to look good on every skin tone.

Nizwa is a bold, bubblegum pink shade. Nizwa is inspired by the beautifully rose gardens of Oman's Jebel Akhdar, or "green mountain" which is located in the city of Nizwa. These gardens are filled with vibrant pink roses that are transformed into the famous Omani rose water.

Baghdad is a sandy beige-nude, opaque in just one coat. This nude color was inspired by the sandy capital of Iraq, Baghdad. Though many of the cultural and historical pieces of the city are gone, there are still some that stand today, like the Al-Khulafa Mosque.
descriptionHtml:
Use Nizwa for a bright baby pink color and add Baghdad for a pretty, nude nail. These two light colors are sure to look good on every skin tone.

Nizwa is a bold, bubblegum pink shade. Nizwa is inspired by the beautifully rose gardens of Oman's Jebel Akhdar, or "green mountain" which is located in the city of Nizwa. These gardens are filled with vibrant pink roses that are transformed into the famous Omani rose water.

Baghdad is a sandy beige-nude, opaque in just one coat. This nude color was inspired by the sandy capital of Iraq, Baghdad. Though many of the cultural and historical pieces of the city are gone, there are still some that stand today, like the Al-Khulafa Mosque.

name: Beirut and Chefchaouen - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Beirut and Chefchaouen - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Beirut is a perfect nude for everyday wear. Use Chefchaouen to give your look a hint of color with the deep blue!

Beirut is a cream pink nude with a warm undertone. This warm nude pink color is inspired by the beautiful and fascinating Lebanese city of Beirut. This amazing city is home to Byzantine Mosaics, extravagant mosques and cathedrals, roman baths, ancient streets, and ruins from the Canaanite and Ottoman eras.

Chefchaouen is a deep and opaque blue-green teal. This blue-green color is inspired by the intricate colors found on the tile art throughout the “Blue pearl” of Morocco, Chefchaouen. This beautiful and mountainous city is famous for its painted blue buildings, a tradition that has lasted over 500 years.

name: Monduli and Top Coat Matte - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Monduli and Top Coat Matte - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Monduli is a great red-pink nail polish to have as a go-to color. Add Top Coat Matte over Monduli or any other 786 Cosmetics color for a chic matte look.

Monduli is a luxurious, rich raspberry color. Monduli is inspired by Lake Natron which is located in the town of Monduli, Tanzania. This lake is rich in minerals, giving the water its stunning red, orange and pink hues.

Top Coat Matte is a quick-drying Top Coat Matte gives your nails a velvety finish but also works to preserve your color and prevent chipping.

name: Samarkand and Lahore - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Samarkand and Lahore - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Are blue nails your go to style? Try Samarkand and Lahore. They both offer beautiful but very different nail looks with Samarkand's deep blue tone and Lahore's light blue-grey color.

Samarkand is a deep indigo-blue. This deep indigo is inspired by the historical Silk Road city, Samarkand. This Uzbekistan city is home to the Gur Emir mausoleum, the Bi-Bi Khanym Moqsue, the medressas of Registan, and the Shah-I-Zinda.

Lahore is a blue-toned gray. This color is inspired by the marble domes of the Badshahi Mosque of Lahore, Pakistan. This 16th century mosque is embellished with stone carvings, red sandstone, and stucco tracery and has a vast square courtyard that can accommodate 100,000 people.

name: Xi'an and Izamal - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Xi'an and Izamal - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Wear Xi'an for an everyday neutral look and add a pop of color with Izamal for a special occasion!

Xi'an is a sleek, smoky steel gray-blue nail polish. Xi'an, China is home to the famous Terracotta Army, known as the starting point of the Silk Road, and is the first city in China to be introduced to Islam.
Izamal is a bold mustard yellow. Two coats to get a full opaque look. This bright and vivid yellow is inspired by the beautiful city in Mexico, Izamal. Nicknamed “La Ciudad Amarilla” (or “The Yellow City”), Izamal is a small town in the state of Yucatan that is famous for its bright yellow buildings.

name: Petra and Lagos - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Petra and Lagos - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Apply Petra for a soft nude tone and add Lagos to give your nails an exciting, colorful blue-green nail look.

Petra is a soft pink nude. One coat provides a translucent look, and two coats make it opaque. Petra is an incredible pre-historic city in Jordan, one of the wonders of the world. Called the "Pink City" because of its carved soft pink cliffs.

Lagos is a deep teal color. This teal nail polish is inspired by the magnificent blue of the Lagos Lagoon in the largest city in Nigerian and Nigerian flag. Lagos is the most populous city in Africa and is one of the fastest growing cities in the world.

name: Hyderabad and Casablanca - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Hyderabad and Casablanca - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Can't decide between a bold pink and a nude pink? Get both! Put on two thin coats of Hyderabad for a bright nail look and use one coat of Casablanca to get a pale nude color!

Hyderabad is a bright hot pink. This vibrant hot pink is inspired by the lively and colorful city of Hyderabad, India. This city provides heritage monuments and museums as a look into the past but has now become a bustling metropolitan.

Casablanca is a pearly light pink. This pearly pink was inspired by the beautiful city of Morocco, Casablanca. The 1942 movie "Casablanca" has branded this city as a romantic location.

name: Jaipur and Lima - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Jaipur and Lima - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
It's clear why these two nail polishes are always sold out. Jaipur is an elegant, yet bold pink that will remind you of the beautiful Pink City and pairs well with the perfect brown nude, Lima.

Jaipur is a deep and bold pink, bright but not hot. Jaipur is inspired by the “the pink city” of India, a color scheme that’s enforced by local law and seen on every building in the city. The Maharaja of Jaipur painted the entire city pink as it was a color that represents welcoming and hospitality.

Lima is a rich, warm brown. This brown color is inspired by the beautiful Peruvian city, Lima. Known as the “city of kings” this city is famous for its food, architecture, and especially the gorgeous coastal landscape. The color was inspired by Lima and Peru’s exceptional coffee beans!

name: Java and Dhofar - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Java and Dhofar - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Java can be used to apply fun nail art designs or to be used as a full color. Dhofar's pretty, shimmer color paid well with Java!

Java is a deeply pigmented onyx black. This opaque black was inspired by the black panthers, or melanistic leopards, found on the Indonesian island of Java. Java is the 13th largest island in the world and formed mostly as a result of volcanic eruptions.

Dhofar is a hot pink cream color, with a hint of shimmer. This shimmering bold pink is inspired by the city Dhofar in Oman. Marco Polo once wrote of Dhofar in his book, calling it a great and noble city and highlighting its frankincense trade - something Dhofar has been famous for since ancient times.

name: Abu Dhabi and Chamarel - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Abu Dhabi and Chamarel - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Abu Dhabi and Chamarel are the cutest pair for anyone who loves bright, fun nails.

Abu Dhabi is a bold white, the creamy texture of the formula provides an opaque look. This creamy white is inspired by the stunning Grand Mosque of Abu Dhabi, U.A.E. The Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque is considered the largest example of marble mosaic in the world.

Chamarel is a bright and bold fuchsia with an opaque finish. This bold fuchsia color is inspired by the village of Chamarel in Mauritius, and specifically its famous natural phenomenon, the Seven Colored Earths.

name: Cordoba and Alexandria - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Cordoba and Alexandria - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Apply Cordoba for a fun, bright pink shade and use Alexandria for a calming pink, beige tone.

Cordoba is a bright warm coral color. This vibrant red hue is inspired by the famous Mezquita of Córdoba, Spain and the annual flower festival hosted there each year in the spring.

Alexandria is a delicate, light pink beige. This pink beige shade is inspired by the Egyptian city of Alexandria, also referred to as the "Pearl of the Mediterranean." It is the largest city on the Mediterranean and is known for its rich culture and ancient history.

name: Sakura and Aswan - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

breadcrumbs.name: Sakura and Aswan - Breathable Nail Polish (2 Piece Set)

description:
Sakura and Aswan are a cute combination and never go out of style. Nude nails will always be on trend, so you can't go wrong with this set!

Sakura is best described as a muted pink nude, nearly opaque with two coats. Sakura is inspired by the stunning pale pink cherry blossoms found in Sakura, Japan. In fact, the most common of all the cherry blossoms are called "Sakura" or Japanese Cherry.

Aswan is best described as a rich, opaque cocoa brown. Aswan is inspired by the historical city of Aswan, Egypt. In Aswan you will find Abu Simbel, incredible massive rock temples that were built by Ramesses II.
